    This class combines SemanticRestriction.ApplyingObjectMinRestriction with the SemanticRestriction.RestrictOnObjectPropertyDomain interface in order to define a restriction of an object property domain within a minimum number of object properties in a given class. It set the SemanticRestriction.ApplyingRestriction.restrictionType to SemanticRestriction.RestrictionType.OBJECT_DOMAIN_MIN_OBJECT. It does not implement any further features rather than the constructors, see the above classes for more details.
